Lvl + refers to the max level of pet that you can tame. One skillmod to rule them all. <b>You can tame level 10 pets at novice.</b> Get a skill above that and you can tame a level 11 pet. Another beside that and you can tame level 12 pets. Another above that and you get up to level 14 pets, etc. This spreads the power-curve from two skill trees to all of the trees, while pushing more benefit to the highest level skill boxes.<br>
